@end example

@findex bfd_log2
@subsubsection @code{bfd_log2}
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
unsigned int bfd_log2 (bfd_vma x);
@end example
@strong{Description}@*
Return the log base 2 of the value supplied, rounded up.  E.g., an
@var{x} of 1025 returns 11.  A @var{x} of 0 returns 0.

